类 InProcessPagesDB

  • java.lang.Object
    • imag.crawler.frontier.WorkQueues
      • imag.crawler.frontier.InProcessPagesDB

  • public class InProcessPagesDB
extends WorkQueues
    This class maintains the list of pages which are assigned to crawlers but are not yet processed. It is used for resuming a previous crawl.
